parameters: This is the place where I first met Kru...
That day, I entered the Sacred Forest searching for the missing Mia...
Even though she hadn't actually gone missing...
And then, finding Kru, my destiny changed...
Since then, so many things have happened...
Umi: "I wonder... was it good for Kru to have met me...?"
If I hadn't met Kru in this place on that day...
Maybe Kru wouldn't have had to suffer...
I can't help but think such things...
??? "The two of them were destined to meet..."
??? "That is something that cannot be changed..."
??? "But there are things that can be changed"

??? "There is definitely hope... as long as there is a strong heart to face
it, there is definitely hope..."
??? "Don't forget the precious feelings of Umi... believe in... fate..."
